        <detaileddescription>
<para>Decomposes a feature to its subfeatures, by calling <computeroutput>func()</computeroutput> on each subfeature. This only returns the direct subfeatures. You can call this recursively to obtain all features, but beware of duplicates (there&apos;s no easy way to filter them). </para>
